# Smart Review Analyzer

An AI-powered website that analyzes customer reviews, identifies sentiment and key themes, and generates professional responses for hospitality businesses.

## Tech Stack

- Frontend: React.js
- Styling: Bootstrap 5
- Backend: Express.js (Node.js)
- Database: MongoDB
- Authentication: JWT Authentication
- AI Integration: Gemini API
- Deployment: Vercel (Frontend) + Render (Backend)

